<!doctype html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title ||= "l33tname" %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="http://yui.yahooapis.com/pure/0.3.0/pure-min.css">
    <style type="text/css">
        html, body {height: 100%;background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #1A1A18; width:100%;}
        .wrapper {
            min-height: 100%;
            height: auto !important;
            height: 100%;
            margin: 0 auto -153px; /*negative von footer height*/
        }
        .footer, .push { height: 153px;} /*muss gleich gross sein wie footer*/ 
        a {color: #A10300; outline: medium none; text-decoration: none;}
        a:hover, a:focus {text-decoration: underline;}
        .banner { background: url('/img/header.jpg') no-repeat fixed 0 0 / cover #1A1A18; display: table; height: 350px; margin-bottom: 5px; text-align: center; width: 100%;}
        .banner-head { color: #FFFFFF; display: table-cell; font-size: 4em; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0; text-shadow: 0 1px 1px #1A1A18; vertical-align: middle;}
        .footer {background-color: #1A1A18; color: #C7C4C1; font-size: 16px; }
        .pure-u-1-3 {width: 33.33%;}
        .pure-u-1-3-c {padding: 0px 15px;}
        .pure-u-1-3-c h5 {text-align: center;}
        .pure-u-1-3-c img {display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;}
        h5 {margin-bottom: 5px;}
        .container {margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; padding-bottom: 20px;}
        .pull-right{float: right;}
        .form input { margin-bottom: 10px;}
        .form textarea { margin-bottom: 10px; height: 100px;}
        p {margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 0px;}
        .aUnstyle {text-decoration: none; color: #FFFFFF;}
        .top-banner{background-color: #C7C4C1; height: 25px;}
        .top-banner a {color: #6B0900;}
        .pure-menu li a {padding-top: 0px;}
        @media (min-device-width:0) and (max-device-width:781px){  
            .footer-hosting{ display: none;}
            .footer-more{ width: 50%; }
            .footer-contact{ width: 50%; }
        }
        @media (min-device-width:0) and (max-device-width:531px){  
            .footer-more{ width: 100%; display: block; padding-top: 1px;}
            .footer-contact{ width: 100%; display: block; }
            .footer, .push { height: 280px;}
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="wrapper">
    <div class="pure-menu pure-menu-open pure-menu-horizontal top-banner">
        <ul>
            <li><a href="http://l33t.name">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="http://blog.l33t.name">Blog</a></li>
            <li><a href="http://movie.l33t.name">Filme</a></li>
            <li><a href="http://portfolio.l33t.name">Portfolio</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="banner">
        <h1 class="banner-head">
            <a href="/" class="aUnstyle"><%= title ||= "l33tname" %></a><br>
            <%= tagline ||= "doing things" %>
        </h1>
    </div>
    <div class="container pure-g-r">
        <%= yield %>
    </div>
    <%= (erb :tracking, :layout => nil) if File.file? File.join(settings.root, "views", "tracking.erb") %>
    <div class="push"></div>
</div>

<div class="footer pure-g-r">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="pure-u-1-3 footer-more">
            <div class="pure-u-1-3-c">
                <h5>Mehr von mir?</h5>
                Dann schau doch mal auf <a href="http://l33t.name">l33t.name</a> vorbei. Oder in meinem "richtigen" Blog <a href="http://l33tsource.com">l33tsource.com</a>. <a href="/impressum">Impressum</a>?
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pure-u-1-3 footer-contact">
            <div class="pure-u-1-3-c">
                <h5>Kontakt & Flattr</h5>
                Schreib einfach ein Mail an: <a href="mailto:blog@l33t.name">blog@l33t.name</a> <br>
                Einfach nur danke sagen? Probier doch mal <a href="https://flattr.com/submit/auto?user_id=Nichtanonymhier&url=http://blog.l33t.name&title=PrimÃ¤rquelle">Flattr</a>.
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pure-u-1-3 footer-hosting">
            <div class="pure-u-1-3-c">
                <h5>Hosting?</h5>
                <a href="http://uberspace.de">
                    <img src="/img/badge-black.png" style="margin-bottom:10px ">
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
